– Warm, elegant, and vintage with a crisp comic-book outline aesthetic

ITEM PLACEMENT:

TEXT LABELS (FOR ITEMS ONLY):

OVERALL LOOK:

– Clean, modern Korean fashion-magazine layout

– Balanced visual spacing

– Final output must match the structure and vibe of the reference images exactly
NEGATIVE PROMPT:

No cartoon, anime, or painterly effects

No alternative backgrounds

No added props

No distorted body parts or clothing shapes
No text or labels on or near the subject
